MANAGEMENT FOR SMALL AND MID-SIZE BUSINESSES, LARGE ORGANIZATIONS, AND DIVISIONS OF GLOBAL ENTERPRISES. REVENUE IS LARGELY DRIVEN BY THE NUMBER OF INFORMATION WORKERS LICENSED.

