WITH SURFACE, INCLUDING A CHARGE FOR SURFACE RT INVENTORY ADJUSTMENTS OF APPROXIMATELY $900 MILLION. THESE COSTS WERE OFFSET IN PART BY A $920 MILLION OR 24% DECREASE IN XBOX PLATFORM COST OF REVENUE, DUE MAINLY TO A DECREASE IN MANUFACTURING AND

DISTRIBUTION COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH LOWER VOLUMES OF XBOX 360 CONSOLES SOLD.

D&C OTHER

