REPURCHASES, A $1.4 BILLION INCREASE IN DIVIDENDS PAID, AND A $324 MILLION DECREASE IN PROCEEDS FROM THE ISSUANCE OF COMMON STOCK, OFFSET IN PART BY A $3.4 BILLION INCREASE IN

