FOR WHICH WE HAVE BEEN PAID IN ADVANCE AND EARN THE REVENUE WHEN WE PROVIDE THE SERVICE OR SOFTWARE, OR OTHERWISE MEET THE REVENUE RECOGNITION CRITERIA.

