SEPTEMBER 22, 2008 AND EXPIRED SEPTEMBER 30, 2013. DURING FISCAL YEARS 2013 AND 2012, WE REPURCHASED 158 MILLION SHARES FOR $4.6 BILLION AND 142 MILLION SHARES FOR $4.0 BILLION, RESPECTIVELY, UNDER THE SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM

ANNOUNCED ON SEPTEMBER 22, 2008. ALL REPURCHASES WERE MADE USING CASH RESOURCES.

